# game/day 13.rpy:304
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_12bbdc92:

    # "Come to think of it,\ndespite Tatsu-nii's huge physique as he sits,\nthe ceiling looks really high."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 461-463)
    "话说回来，\n体格庞大的辰兄即使坐下来了也还是一样的高大，\n这一点让天花板看上去更高了啊。"

# game/day 13.rpy:308
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_b8c6f30b:

    # su "「[fn]-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 469-470)
    su "「[博行]桑？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:312
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_892fc6de:

    # ta "「What's the matter?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 473-474)
    ta "「怎么了？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:313
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_5c7f691a:

    # fn "「Oh, well.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 476-477)
    fn "「啊，没什么。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:314
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_ebe26622:

    # "They noticed me looking around restlessly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 479)
    "两个人的眼神看来就是十分在意的样子。"

# game/day 13.rpy:315
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_b11ff85e:

    # fn "「Umm, I was thinking about how big \n your grandfather's house is, Shun-kun.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 481-483)
    fn "「嗯，就是觉得峻君的祖父家\n真的很大啊。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:319
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_7dfe9635:

    # su "「Hehe♪ The Carpenters of Minasato\n built it for him.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 488-489)
    su "「嘿嘿，　是水乡的工匠们建造的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:320
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_d669b99d:

    # fn "「Oh, really?{w=.2} That means Tatsu-nii did it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 491-493)
    fn "「啊，是这样喔？　那就是辰兄你们盖的？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:321
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_e2d9f466:

    # ta "「No, it wasn't the Midoriya Group.{p} I specialize in shrines.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 494-495)
    ta "「不是，不是翠屋组，我们是木匠啊。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:322
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_87484b23:

    # ta "「They're not in the village anymore.{p} They're an old acquaintance of my family.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 497-499)
    ta "「虽然现在是已经离开村子了，\n不过跟我们是从以前就认识的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:323
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_d2599075:

    # su "「The master at the time was introduced\n to my grandfather's grandfather's\n grandfather's grandfather.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 501-504)
    su "「两边有互相介绍过，\n我爷爷的爷爷的爷爷的爷爷，\n是那时候的栋梁。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:324
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_f8f5ceae:

    # fn "「E-err, say that again please.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 506-507)
    fn "「那、那个，请再说一次。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:325
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_2a29f09b:

    # su "「It's a story of the Kodori family and the\n Minasato Group from 8 generations ago.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 509-510)
    su "「距离现在是八代以前的，古酉家和水乡组的事了。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:326
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_f67f9603:

    # ta "「Their way of constructing was different from ours.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 512-513)
    ta "「建造的方法跟我们所用的不一样，"

# game/day 13.rpy:327
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_a2431bf9:

    # ta "「They just had long-lasting techniques and care\nover the particulars.{w} After all, that was\n the spirit of the Carpenters of Minasato.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 514-515)
    ta "有这种坚固的建筑技术再加上那种坚持，\n这果然就是水乡工匠的个性啊。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:328
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_609200cd:

    # "Ooh, Tatsu-nii has an unusually serious expression."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 517)
    "喔喔，辰兄露出这种认真的表情还真是稀奇啊。"

# game/day 13.rpy:329
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_eae42437:

    # "The apprentice gazes in awe at the pillars and beams.{p}Then that expression seems to change\nto pride in his occupation."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 518-519)
    "那敬畏的视线所注目的，是有着相当年纪的梁柱。\n会有那样的目光变化是因为对工作的骄傲吧。"

# game/day 13.rpy:330
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_b4048244:

    # fn "「Really? That's amazing.{p} It won't budge for 100 or even 200 years.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 521-523)
    fn "「这样啊，真厉害啊。\n即使过了一两百年也完全不曾动摇过吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:331
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_87aea48c:

    # ta "「I know, I'll teach you all about\n the greatness of the Carpenters of Minasato!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 526-527)
    ta "难得有这机会，我就让[博行]你知道水乡工匠的厉害吧！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:332
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 529-530)
    fn "「诶？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:337
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_729f80d5:

    # ta "「First!{w=.2} No matter who gets on the roof\n of their buildings, it'll never break!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 534-536)
