# game/day 13.rpy:393
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_67fcebf9:

    # "Tatsu-nii crosses his arms and nods in satisfaction.{p}Shun-kun is unable to hide his astonishment\nat the sight stretching out.{w} Yeah, yeah."
