    # ta "「Nah, you don't sound convinced,\n so I'll do it until I'm satisfied.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 687-689)
    ta "「不行，那种说法就是还没认同对吧，\n一定要让你完全认同才会停的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:421
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_c49d8d3b:

    # "Tatsu-nii isn't satisfied!?"
