    "辰兄就这个样子不停地重复跳着。\n呜哇哇，站的地方摇摇晃晃的啊……\n[漏れ]就在原地坐了下来。"

# game/day 13.rpy:447
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_cfc9eb90:

    # su "「Hawawaah, I'm shaking.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 719-720)
    su "「哇哇哇，在摇晃啊……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:458
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_0be0a60e:

    # "When I look over, Shun-kun is also on all fours\nand is somehow keeping his balance.{p}B-{w=.2}but..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 728-730)
    "峻君用着两只手贴在屋顶上的姿势，\n来保持身体的平衡。\n不、不过……"

# game/day 13.rpy:469
translate chinese_simplified shun13_carpenters_1049cc9b:

    # "Shun-kun's body is so light that\nwhenever it shakes, he flies up.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/峻_s_01.ks (KS 741)
