translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_5a0424e5:

    # "I see, that's why these guys are here.{p}Two are in sports clubs,\nand then there's Tatsu-nii..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 99-100)
    "原来如此，所以才会找来这些体格强壮的人啊。\n运动部的两人，还有在大家之中个子最大的辰兄。"

# game/day 13.rpy:717
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_656d1ef2:

    # "Wait, how did I end up getting called?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 101)
    "阿勒，那[漏れ]到底是……？"

# game/day 13.rpy:718
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_daf947ff:

    # fn "「Why was I called over?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 103-104)
    fn "\n「[漏れ]为什么会被叫来呢？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:722
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_f33cec93:

    # bo "「Because you had the most free time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 107-108)
    bo "\n「因为你是看上去最空闲嘛」"

# game/day 13.rpy:723
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_39a23b2d:

    # bo "「And, after being in the city for so long,\n I thought you'd appreciate the countryside.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 110-112)
    bo "\n「而且难得你回来一趟，\n想让你充分体验农村生活。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:724
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_2317b97a:

    # bo "「Juuichi can still do judo when it's raining,\n and isn't Kouya a little far away?{p} That's why you're the fourth one here.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 114-117)
    bo "\n「柔一参加的活动部就算下雨了也能照常进行活动\n洸哉也离这里很远吧？\n所以你就是第四个男人了。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:725
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_b6daeeac:

    # "Urgh... I suppose it's true I'm free every day.{p}Of all of us, I'm the most available."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 119-120)
    "唔咕……确实每天都很有空。\n在大家之中最懒懒散散的呢。"

# game/day 13.rpy:726
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_50bd4740:

    # bo "「We'll take a car over. Time to go.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 122-123)
    bo "\n「会开车送到家门口的啦，喂出发了----」"

# game/day 13.rpy:727
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_c6d78ae5:

    # "So we'll be working in the rain.{p}Man, what a drag..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 125-126)
