    # farmer "「Everyone has so much energy...{p} I have high hopes for you all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 145-146)
    farmer "\n「大家看上去都很精神呢……那么，期待你们今天的努力工作哦」"

