# game/day 13.rpy:764
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_600c4d5a:

    # "In the old days I ran around the fields with\neveryone, and we'd keep going until we dropped.{p}Harvesting surely can't compare to that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 180-182)
    "以前[漏れ]也和大家一起在野地上到处跑。\n每天都玩到没力气为止。\n这样程度的原野工作可轻松了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:765
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_f8568ab7:

    # "Besides, why am I the only one to get something\ndifferent?{p}I can't have that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 184-185)
    "而且如果只让[漏れ]去做些其他的事情的话，\n那也实在是太悲剧了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:766
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_dedaba6d:

    # farmer "「Really? Do your best, then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 187-188)
    farmer "\n「是这样啊，那就努力干吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:767
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_3bc95249:

    # fn "「Yes, I'll give it all I've got!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 190-191)
