# game/day 13.rpy:768
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_f6dcee8c:

    # "Watch as I surpass the old man's expectations!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 193)
    "看着吧，[漏れ]会让大叔大吃一惊的！"

# game/day 13.rpy:776
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_b5c4a3c7:

    # farmer "「To start with, can you do the plowing?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 197-198)
    farmer "\n「那，上午就帮我把这里给耕好吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:777
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_dcba3028:

    # farmer "「Since there are four of you,\n you can all take one field each.{p} We'll have lunch when you finish.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 200-203)
    farmer "\n「既然有4个人在这，就将那边的田地，\n一人一道，一直到那边尽头为止，帮我耕好吧\n干完的人就回来吃午饭吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:778
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_ffed5e01:

    # farmer "「It should only take about that long.{p} We'll have a break after lunch, and then you'll\n do something else on the opposite fields.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 205-207)
