# game/day 13.rpy:797
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_39754635:

    # "Maybe I should've gone with packing boxes...{p}No, I am also a man.{w} Tell me to do it,\nand I will.{w} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 233-234)
    "果然还是应该叫大叔让[漏れ]去装箱子……不，[漏れ]也是个男人。\n既然都说出口了，就豁出去了。全力去耕地吧！"

# game/day 13.rpy:799
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_outside_b6854bac:

    # extend " I'll plough the hell out of this thing!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 234)
    extend "既然都说出口了，就豁出去了。全力去耕地吧！"

