    # fn "「Hey, why don't we make this a competition?{p} Last one done treats the others to juice.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 236-238)
    fn "\n「好吧，大家来比谁第一个最快把地耕完吧。\n谁最后一名就请大家喝果汁。」"

