translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_inside_95e7f9d2:

    # "This is simple enough that even I can do it.{p}It sucks that everyone else is working in the rain.{p}I wonder if I'm good enough to work out there?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 297-299)
    "这样的话[漏れ]也能轻松完成工作呢。\n大家都在外面淋着雨工作真是抱歉呢\n[漏れ]是不是也应该和大家一起在外面工作呢。"

# game/day 13.rpy:851
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_inside_e0100377:

    # ow "「Are you a student?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 301-302)
    ow "\n「小兄弟你是学生么？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:852
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_inside_fc49512e:

    # fn "「Yes, I am.{p} I grew up here, but we moved,\n and now I live in the city.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 304-307)
