    # "Tatsu-nii yelled out,\nand began advancing with the cart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 831-832)
    "\n「虽然那也是个麻烦，不过在水里凹凸不平才是问题呢。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1174
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_464230f6:

    # to "「Cart wheels are pretty hard to move underwater,\n but they're not as bad as I thought they'd be.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 835-836)
    to "「好像变得很重了呢，\n现在应该到了水潭的正中间的某处了吧？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1175
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_8e4787dd:

    # ky "「True, but remember that the ground might not\n be level under the surface.\n That could be a problem.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 838-839)
    ky "走到这地方就已经很泥泞不堪，颠簸难行，\n现在很难如愿地继续前进了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1176
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_4bfa9169:

    # fn "「It's getting harder to move it.\n Have we reached the center yet?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 842-843)
    fn "\n「还差一点点而已，加把劲吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1177
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_effc0b30:

    # "Our footing is getting worse after coming this\nfar through the mud,\nand it's getting harder to advance."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 847-848)
    "\n「唔，这是什么！？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1181
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_048b5c09:

    # ta "「Just a little more! Keep going!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 850-851)
    ta "\n「大島，发生什么事？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1187
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_e57bc594:

    # to "「Right.{w=.2} Wait, what!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 853-855)
    to "\n「是不是下面有石头……？\n好像被什么东西给卡住了似的」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1188
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_93052c08:

    # ky "「Ooshima, what's wrong?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 857-859)
    ky "无论我们如何推动，货架车都不前进分毫。\n随着我们反复的又推又拉，\n只有时间在这雨中慢慢的流逝着……"

# game/day 13.rpy:1189
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_617a9393:

    # fn "「Is there a rock, or something...?{p} It looks like it's stuck on something.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 862-864)
    fn "\n「一直在这里卡着也无济于事。\n配合时机用力，无论怎样都要越过这里。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1190
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_e82e448c:

    # "Stuck in the rain, no matter how much we tried,\nthe cart wouldn't move.{w} We even tried pulling\nbackwards, but time was the only thing moving."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 866-867)
    "\n「嗯，知道了。试试吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1194
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_98c7fd6d:

    # ta "「There's no helping it, we're stuck here.{p} But, if we push with all our strength at the same\n time, we can overcome anything.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 869-870)
    ta "\n「那准备好了吗？ 　开始咯。嘿~哟」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1195
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_c2a01d24:

    # fn "「Hm, okay.{w} Let's try that, then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 873-874)
    fn "\n「呵呀呀呀呀呀呀」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1196
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_735b47b0:

    # ky "「Ready?{w} Let's go.{w} One, two...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 876)
    ky "虽然[漏れ]一起向货架车施力，但是货架车还是一动也不动"

# game/day 13.rpy:1200
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_5fdb4086:

    # ta "{size=+15}「Hiyaaaaaah!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 878-879)
    ta "\n「推不动呀……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1201
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_982ad126:

    # "We all pushed together at once,\nbut the cart didn't budge."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 881-882)
    "\n「再来一次」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1202
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_73c5d4ba:

    # fn "「It won't move...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 884-885)
    fn "\n「唔唔唔唔唔……这次好像能行」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1203
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_e9ffb398:

    # ta "「Let's try again.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 887-888)
    ta "\n「大島！　你那边倾斜了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1204
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_6afd2e0f:

    # fn "「Hmm... It feels like something might move,\n this time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 891-892)
    fn "\n「知道啦，只要不倒下来就行了吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1205
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_18f18a67:

    # ky "「Ooshima!{w} It's tilting that way.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 894-895)
    ky "\n「还差一口气了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1209
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_f8637d87:

    # to "「Got it, it'll be fine as long as it doesn't\n go too far, right?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 897-898)
    to "\n「成功了吗？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1210
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_16a01456:

    # fn "「Just a little more...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 901-902)
    fn "\n「没问题，已经没有被什么卡住了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1211
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_9522e634:

    # ky "「Did it get free?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 904-906)
    ky "\n\n「就这样下去，一口气走出水潭吧！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1215
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_480d5b58:

    # to "「It's fine. It's not caught on anything now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 901-902)
    to "\n「没问题，已经没有被什么卡住了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1219
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_tatsuki_aac02c40:

    # ta "「At this rate, we'll be done in no time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 904-906)
    ta "\n\n「就这样下去，一口气走出水潭吧！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1234
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_4ff9840f:

    # fn "「Kyouji-senpai, what do you think we should do?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 919)
    fn "「京慈前辈觉得应该怎样？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1235
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_e846e8b6:

    # "He is a senior, after all..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 921)
    "这里就听听为大家担任总结的京慈前辈怎么说吧。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1236
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_7758d9bc:

    # ky "「I think we'd be better off carrying things\n separately, rather than forcing our way through.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 924-925)
    ky "「我觉得比起鲁莽地冒着风险前进，\n安全地运过去更好。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1240
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_99e18710:

    # ta "「Well... it's annoying, but we do have time,\n and we'd certainly get it done that way.{p} I wanna do this quickly since it's raining, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 928-931)
    ta "\n「唔~嘛，虽然很麻烦又多少会花多点时间，\n确实能运过去的话当然就好。\n虽然本来想着下雨想快点干完结束的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1244
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_ad653d7c:

    # to "「It's not like we can do anything about that.{p} Isn't there a shortcut or something?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 934-935)
    to "\n「没办法。这附近哪里有近道吗？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1245
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_a6965da7:

    # fn "「Isn't this the fastest way through already?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 937-938)
    fn "\n「这里不就是最近的近道了么。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1246
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_6ca50954:

    # ky "「Now that you mention it,\n Ooshima led us this way to begin with...{p} Let's try taking a different route.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 940-943)
    ky "\n「说起来，是大島说要往这边\n走的……。\n你该不会想着走近道，觉得连这种不平的小道都可以吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1252
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_c8937b04:

    # fn "「That reminds me. When we came into the fields,\n wasn't the road wider?\n It felt like a good path to walk.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 948-950)
    fn "\n「说起来[漏れ]觉得[漏れ]们来田地时走的道路是\n比这条路更宽广，很容易通过的才对啊」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1253
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_fc85616c:

    # ta "「Oh, Tora... when we were young you'd say 'let's\n take a shortcut', come to a crazy conclusion and\n get mad, then go with it anyway.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 954-957)
    ta "\n「你呀……以前不是说着要走近道，\n跑进了不知道是哪里的地方还被人骂了，\n结果花了更多不必要的时间吗。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1254
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_b78136af:

    # ta "「You haven't learned from experience, have you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 959-960)
    ta "\n「到现在还没吸取一点教训啊」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1255
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_a68b1195:

    # fn "「That's right. Whether it was your own garden,\n a fence we needed to climb, or even a grass field,\n you'd ford rivers and climb mountains to avoid it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 962-965)
    fn "\n「对对，别人家庭院的院墙上面之类的，\n根本看不见立足处的草丛里、水渠之类的，\n在山里面横穿一座山之类的也干过呢。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1256
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_84f73d5b:

    # ky "「The ones who followed Torahiko in high spirits\n were Tatsuki-san and [fn], from memory...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 967-969)
    ky "\n「就这样跟着虎彦走的人，\n应该只有辰树和[博行]了吧……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1257
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_2eba8ca1:

    # fn "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 971-972)
    fn "\n「是这样吗？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1261
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_c5c181bd:

    # to "「No, I didn't think it'd turn out like this.{p} Besides, if something did happen,\n there were the four of us...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 975-977)
    to "\n「呀，因为没想到道路会变成这样嘛。\n就算有什么事也有4个人在这里……"

# game/day 13.rpy:1262
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_3f1db5ee:

    # ky "「Well, there's no helping it.\n Looks like we'll have to double back.{p} I think it's best we try a different road.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 979-981)
    ky "\n「没办法，总之先返回吧。\n我觉得走别的路会更好。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1266
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_2c7bc8e7:

    # ta "「With three people, we should be able to handle it,{p} but we can't do the impossible, I suppose.\n Later, Tora.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 984-987)
    ta "\n「虽然东西很多，不过所谓三个臭皮匠也顶个诸葛亮，\n但是没必要去做毫无道理的事呢。\n那再见了，虎」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1267
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_3aabbea7:

    # fn "「If we turn back now, we'll at least get all these\n in safely.{w} Nice job, Torahiko.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 989-990)
    fn "\n「总而言之回去的话能安全地运过去呢。辛苦了虎彦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1271
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_bd0a33a3:

    # to "「Hey, you two. What are you leaving me alone for?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 993-994)
    to "\n「喂，你们俩。干嘛把我丢在这里啊。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1272
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_1cd9f3ee:

    # ky "「Ooshima, it's fine if they\n go ahead and take a break.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1000-1001)
    ky "\n「怎能这样。连京慈前辈都这样」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1276
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_07e4ebc1:

    # to "「Aw, geez.{w} Not you too, Kyouji-senpai!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 996-997)
    to "\n「大岛，先休息一下也行哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1277
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_8a5e4ee0:

    # ky "「Hmph,{w=.2} come help with this thing aready.{p} Or I really will leave you behind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1003-1004)
    ky "\n「呼，快点过来。真的要丢下你一个人走了哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1282
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_d9351be4:

    # ta "「As punishment for taking a shortcut, you don't\n get to eat today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1008-1009)
    ta "\n「作为你今天想要走近道的惩罚，你今天没晚饭吃哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1286
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_f89f8d05:

    # fn "「Because you made Mom and Dad angry, right?{p} Now stand over there and think about what you did.{p} I'll let you back in once you think it over.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1012-1015)
    fn "\n「爸爸和妈妈都生气了哦。\n在你反省之前就站在那吧。\n只要你反省了就让你进家门。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1290
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_4426f882:

    # to "「Who're you guys again?{w} Damnit, you'd better\n remember this. Next time you screw up, I'll be\n there to laugh at you guys...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1018-1020)
    to "\n「你们算是谁呀，可恶，给我记着。\n要是你们失败了的话，我可要戏弄你们到你们厌烦的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1291
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_f031357d:

    # ta "「Isn't the one laughing always the same guy?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1022-1023)
    ta "\n「被谁戏弄什么的不是家常便饭么」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1292
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_6465365b:

    # fn "「Ahahahaha! You're lucky Kouya's not here today.{p} If he were, you'd be getting a verbal thrashing\n right around now.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1025-1027)
    fn "\n「啊哈哈哈哈，今天洸哉不在真是太好了呢。\n要是在的话你现在不是会被说的很惨么？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1296
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_kyouji_7ce4d3ae:

    # to "{size=+15}「DAMNIT!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1030-1031)
    to "\n「可恶！！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1310
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_6b2bb1b1:

    # fn "「Since you move heavy things every day at work,\n won't you be fine, Tatsu-nii?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1040-1041)
    fn "「辰兄的话每天工作时都在搬运很重的东西，\n应该没问题吧？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1311
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_27251268:

    # "It's overkill, maybe, but I agree with Torahiko.{p}Rather than let an amateur butt in, it'd be better\nto leave things to a professional."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1043-1044)
    "虽然觉得有点太轻率了，[漏れ]也赞成虎彦说的。\n比起让门外汉乱来，交给专家的话比较安心。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1315
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_4ca70ab5:

    # to "「Right, right.{w} If Tatsu-nii uses his giant body\n and power, moving this should be no problem.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1047-1049)
    to "\n「就是呀。只要有辰兄巨大的身体和力量的话，\n这种程度很简单的啦。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1319
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_03fc5633:

    # ta "「Y-{w=.2}you think?{w} Well, there's nothing I can't do.{p} {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1052-1053)
    ta "\n「是，是这样吗。嘛这也不是办不到的事。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1321
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_1876af80:

    # extend "So all four of us going together is a bad plan?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1054-1055)
    extend "比起一个人来干,\n大家一起推不是更好吗？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1322
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_8e1b19fb:

    # ky "「If we all went together, wouldn't that mean\n that we can't leave it all to you, Tatsuki-san?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1057-1059)
    ky "\n「“要是大家一起推”这样的话就别说了,\n其实也没必要全交给辰樹一个人去干吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_22085754:

    # ta "「Well, no, it's not like I need your help.\n I think one person should be able to do it alone.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1062-1064)
    ta "\n「不不，其实就算不用你们帮忙,\n我觉得我一个人也能办得到的啦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1330
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_529082fd:

    # to "「That settles it.{p} If it's Tatsu-nii, it should be fine.\n Now let's try that out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1067-1068)
    to "\n「那就这样决定吧。辰兄的话肯定没问题，去试试吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1331
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_3245108f:

    # fn "「When it comes down to it, you get dependable.\n That's so awesome.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1070-1071)
    fn "\n「这种时候很可靠哦，真帅呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1332
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_2620cd8c:

    # "If it's Tatsu-nii... if it's up to him...{p}He should be able to do it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1073-1074)
    "是辰兄的话……这种时候是辰兄的话……。\n应该是无论如何都能办得到的。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1336
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_45309328:

    # ta "「No way around it... right, leave it to me.{p} I'll show you what a real man is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1077-1079)
    ta "\n「没办法……好吧交给我了。\n给你们看看什么叫男子汉。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1337
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_49251e0a:

    # ky "「Is this okay...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1081-1082)
    ky "\n「没问题吧……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1338
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_c0772526:

    # "Tatsu-nii's getting interested in this, and it\nreally looks like he'll be able to do it himself.{p}Too bad we aren't all helping, but oh well."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1084-1086)
    "辰兄也变得起劲了，看起来一个人也能办得到呢。\n要是不行的话大家再一起推也行。\n嗯，nice idea。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1348
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_b65e3f6f:

    # ta "「All right, let's go! Uoooooo!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1092-1093)
    ta "\n「好了要上咯。唔啊啊啊啊啊啊」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1352
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_f2d8ebfa:

    # "The cart's moving slowly, but it is moving forward."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1096)
    "货架开始慢慢地向前动了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1353
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_afbe1490:

    # fn "「It moved!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1098-1099)
    fn "\n「动了~！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1354
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_bb157a69:

    # to "「I believe Tatsu-nii could do anything for us.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1102-1103)
    to "\n「我就相信是辰兄就肯定会有办法做到的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1359
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_617c5097:

    # ta "「Heheh,{w=.2} This is actually pretty easy.{p} ...Oh wait, what?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1107-1109)
    ta "\n「嘻嘻，这种程度太轻松了。\n……啊呀呀，怎么回事？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1360
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_68bc4b9c:

    # fn "「Tatsu-nii, look out!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1111-1112)
    fn "\n「辰兄，危险！！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1361
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_3ac16db6:

    # "Tatsu-nii seems to have stumbled on something,\ntipping him off-balance and making him flail wildly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1114-1115)
    "好像被什么东西给绊到了，\n辰兄因为失去平衡而大幅度地摇晃着。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1367
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_fac64a59:

    # ta "「Whoa, thisisbad!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1119-1120)
    ta "\n「啊，糟糕。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1372
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_1c70b8d3:

    # fn "「That was a really dramatic fall, are you okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1125-1126)
    fn "\n「好像摔得很厉害，没事吧？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1377
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_c411d2ac:

    # to "「Crap! At this rate the cart's gonna tip over!{p} Umm??{w} The cart's gonna fall, because Tatsu-nii\n fell over???」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1130-1132)
    to "\n「糟糕，这样下去的话货架要倒了。\n唔？？　货架摔倒后辰兄也要倒下了？？？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1378
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_04030cd4:

    # ky "「Ooshima, it's the other way round.{p} Anyway, we need to do something about that cart.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1134-1136)
    ky "\n「大島，反了反了。\n总而言之，先想办法稳住货架」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1379
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_5e944faf:

    # "In the moment Tatsu-nii fell over, the cart really\nlurched. It looked like it would topple sideways]nat any moment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1138-1139)
    "随着辰兄摔倒货架也在大幅度地倾斜着，\n现在像是随时都能翻倒过来似的。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1380
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_e5b1f4c3:

    # "The three of us tried our hardest to right it,\nbut even with our best efforts...\nThe cart still tipped over."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1141-1142)
    "[漏れ]们3人想让货架恢复平衡，\n虽然努力想要做点什么……但货架还是在倾斜着。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1384
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_83562f5a:

    # to "「Crap, it looks like the vegetables\n are gonna be crushed!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1145-1146)
    to "\n「糟糕，蔬菜好像快要掉下来了。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1385
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_3caa8c5b:

    # fn "「I... can't do anymore...{w=.2} I'm at my limit...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1148-1149)
    fn "\n「已经……不行了，极限了……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1389
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_36f6211a:

    # ta "「My bad. Hang on, I'll fix this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1152-1153)
    ta "\n「抱歉，我马上来帮忙。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1390
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_00776846:

    # "The fallen Tatsu-nii got up,\nthen closed his powerful hands on the cart."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1155-1156)
    "摔倒的辰兄站了起来，\n双手用力地推向货架。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1396
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_8bb6bed2:

    # to "「Tatsu-nii, you're pushing it the wrong waaay!!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1160-1161)
    to "\n「辰兄，你推的方向反了---！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1403
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_2d295345:

    # fn "「Aw, man. It collapsed.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1168-1169)
    fn "\n「啊~啊，倒了……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1407
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_25f34410:

    # to "「Well, if we wash the vegetables off,\n they should be all right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1172-1173)
    to "\n「虽然蔬菜只要洗洗的话应该是没问题的」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1408
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_65211d6b:

    # ky "「It's no use.\n We're going to have to apologise for this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1175-1176)
    ky "\n「只能去道歉了吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1412
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_f0a10d94:

    # ta "「We came over to help out,\n but we somehow forgot that along the way...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1180-1181)
    ta "「我们到底是来帮忙的，\n还是来干什么的都已经搞不清楚了……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1413
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_e87484e2:

    # "Sigh...{p}This plan really needed more forethought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1183-1184)
    "哎……为什么总是在事情发生过了才感到后悔啊。\n果然应该好好地考虑之后再行动啊。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1417
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_79f32eee:

    # "In the end, we went off to apologise."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1187)
    "结果，[漏れ]们去道歉了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1418
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_torahiko_70d89324:

    # "The farmer was pretty forgiving,\nbut Botan-sensei really gave us an earful.{p}(As the one responsible, Torahiko got it worst.)"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1189-1191)
    "虽然大叔的反应倒是还好，\n不过还是遇上了好久没见过的被牡丹老师狠狠地骂一顿的窘境……\n（主谋者虎彦被骂得最惨）"

# game/day 13.rpy:1433
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_d50398b0:

    # fn "「We've finished.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1206-1207)
    fn "\n「终于结束了~~」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1434
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_2b47e125:

    # farmer "「Thank you for your work today.{p} You've been so much help. The day's almost over,\n so come on inside and rest.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1209-1211)
    farmer "\n「辛苦了。看来很好干完了呢，帮大忙了。\n今天的工作已经结束了，到我家里来休息一下吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1435
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b673ce46:

    # fn "「Okay. Good work, everyone.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1213-1214)
    fn "\n「是啊，大家都很努力。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1436
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_888847ef:

    # "We were all so completely exhausted from work,\nwe accepted his invitation without second thought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1216-1217)
    "[漏れ]们因为劳动已经十分疲倦了，\n所以不客气地接受了招待，到主人家去了。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1437
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_ce4d9ffc:

    # fn "「Whew, we're finally done.{p} When we took Torahiko's 'shortcut' at the end,\n I was wondering how that would turn out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1219-1222)
    fn "\n「唉，总算结束了。\n在最后虎彦想要走近道，\n站着不知所措的时候还以为事情会变成怎样呢 」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1441
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_c3138b39:

    # to "「It's not my fault the weather sucks.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1226-1227)
    to "\n「那不是我的错，是天气不好」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1445
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_4a319a36:

    # ky "「Haha. At any rate,\n it's great that it all ended up with no problems.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1231-1233)
    ky "\n「哈哈，不管怎么说，\n平安结束真是太好了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1449
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b26c8dcc:

    # ta "「Even on a day off I have to do work.{p} I'm so tired...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1237-1239)
    ta "\n「不过在休息日里干力气活很费劲啊。\n累了……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1450
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_fc85b7f8:

    # fn "「So even you get tired.{p} I've got this image of you never getting tired.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1241-1243)
    fn "\n「辰兄也是会累的啊，\n虽然在印象中你完全不会感觉到累的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1454
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_8bade520:

    # ta "「Of course I get tired, I'm not a machine.{p} For now I'm okay, but for tomorrow...{p} Tch.{w=.2} I'm jealous of you guys on Summer vacation.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1246-1249)
    ta "\n「我又不是机械，当然会感觉到累了。\n今天还好，到了明天的话……。\n切真羡慕你们有暑假。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1455
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_0b5a9533:

    # ky "「The rain gave me a day off today,\n but there'll probably be club activities tomorrow.\n It's probably going to be intense, to make up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1251-1253)
    ky "\n「虽然今天是下雨才中止的，\n不过明天应该会有社团活动，所以还是有点辛苦呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1459
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_8fd3627f:

    # to "「I have club tomorrow, too,\n so I'm jealous of the people with time to spare.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1256-1257)
    to "\n「我明天也有社团活动，真羡慕闲人呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1460
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_fabac6b2:

    # fn "「I have to guard my house, and that means\n patrolling the perimeter. Man, I'm so busy...{p} Wait,{w=.2} it's not my house. It's Grandpa's.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1259-1262)
    fn "\n「[漏れ]也有在自己家附近巡逻的，\n啊啊很忙呢……]\n啊不是自己家而是爷爷家才对」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1464
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_389636bb:

    # to "「What the hell is that about?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1265-1266)
    to "\n「那算什么呀」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1465
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b46edf43:

    # everyone "「Hahahahahaha!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1268)
    everyone "「哈哈哈哈哈哈」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1466
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_5f61a5da:

    # "It doesn't look like we'll be able to hang out\nafter this, we're just all too tired.{p}Plus, it's started to rain again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1270-1271)
    "今天，已经累得等下想玩也玩不成了呢。\n而且又在下雨。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1467
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_0539bec3:

    # "In any case, I'm glad we're done with helping out.{p}I'm probably gonna be all sore tomorrow..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1273-1274)
    "总而言之能帮忙解决问题真是太好了。\n这样的话明天应该会肌肉酸痛的吧……"

# game/day 13.rpy:1468
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_336b2434:

    # ow "「Thank you so much for everything, boys.{p} Go take the vegetables into the kitchen to cool,\n and then make sure to eat as much as you like.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1276-1279)
    ow "\n「小伙子们，今天真是谢谢了呀。\n我家摘取的蔬菜已经放在厨房的桶里凉着了，\n不用客气尽管吃吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1469
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_523e6025:

    # ky "「Thank you very much.{p} Sorry for intruding,\n especially after we came over to help.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1281-1283)
    ky "\n「谢谢。\n不好意思啊我们明明是来帮忙的。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1470
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_80e52366:

    # ow "「It's no trouble at all. Now, go on, eat up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1285-1286)
    ow "\n「没事啦，不用客气尽管吃哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1471
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_e8cdbd13:

    # fn "「Thank you very much... whoa,{w=.2} these look tasty!{p} Are they okay? They're still soaking.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1289-1290)
    fn "「谢谢……呜哇看上去好像很好吃！\n一直冲着水没关系吗」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1472
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_84575a69:

    # "Inside the kitchen sink was a bucket of water.\nInside the bucket were a bunch of tomatoes and\ncucumbers, all floating around."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1292-1293)
    "厨房里有个正在注水的桶，\n桶中的水面上浮着许多黄瓜和番茄。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1473
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_d8e9b032:

    # "Water was flowing into the bucket from a tap,\nand I was feeling chilled just by looking at it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1295-1296)
    "水流源源不断地注入桶中，\n光是看着就有种凉爽的感觉。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1474
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_ac6d0ab3:

    # ow "「That water is drawn from a mountain spring, so it\n never stops flowing.{w} Sometimes it's a little\n bit dirty, but that's nothing to worry about.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1298-1301)
    ow "\n「那个呀，是从山上引下来的水所以不会停啦。\n虽然偶然也有出水出得不太顺的时候，\n不过因为是免费的所以不用在意哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1478
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_ced52f7d:

    # ta "「They're so good when they're cold.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1304-1305)
    ta "\n「凉的正好，很好吃哦」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1479
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_8d27c413:

    # "While I was talking with the farmer's wife,\nTatsu-nii stepped over and bit into a tomato."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1307-1308)
    "[漏れ]和阿姨说话的时候，\n辰兄比谁都快一步地把番茄放在嘴里大口大口地吃起来。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1480
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_396041c9:

    # ky "「Tatsu-nii, aren't you eating a bit fast...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1310-1311)
    ky "\n「辰兄，现在吃不会太快了吗……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1481
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_bbdd191e:

    # ow "「Now now, don't you worry, boys.\n Eat fast or it'll all be gone.{w} I need to finish\n up some things, but go ahead and relax.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1313-1316)
    ow "\n「快快，其他几个小伙子也不用客气了，\n会被吃光的哦。\n我还有事情要做先离开一下，慢慢吃吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1482
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_f23bc6e6:

    # "In that case, I'll have one too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1318)
    "那[漏れ]也不客气咯~。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1483
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_81b6bb20:

    # "...?!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1320)
    "……！？"

# game/day 13.rpy:1484
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_83edbb67:

    # fn "「This tomato is awesome!{p} It's so sweet, you wouldn't need to pickle it.{p} Vegetables like this are so delicious!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1322-1325)
    fn "\n「这个番茄好好吃啊。\n好甜呀，这样的话什么都不加也没问题呢。\n蔬菜原来这么好吃啊！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1488
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_4fddea5c:

    # ta "「Gahaha! You can't get fresh stuff like this\n in the city, can you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1328-1329)
    ta "\n「噶哈哈，在城里的话很少吃这种东西吧。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1489
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_85447702:

    # fn "「No, you can't.\n It's like I'm eating a different food.{p} Surprising.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1331-1332)
    fn "\n「真的是这样，就像是在吃别的东西一样。吓了一跳呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1493
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_3cc618a8:

    # to "「It's good, but there're only cucumbers and\n tomatoes...{w} It'd be nice if there were\n some other things, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1335-1337)
    to "\n「虽然是很好吃啦，就是只有番茄和黄瓜啊……。\n要是稍微有点别的东西的话就好了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1494
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_a845a9b1:

    # fn "「That would be luxury. I'm fine with just these.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1339-1340)
    fn "\n「要求的太多了吧。[漏れ]只有这些就已经满足了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1495
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_977db251:

    # ky "「Well, there are other vegetables.\n we could ask to chill some lettuce, or some\n eggplant, but you can't eat that raw.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1342-1345)
    ky "\n「要是说别的蔬菜什么的，\n就算放了凉的茄子和卷心菜之类的，\n生的也根本没法吃嘛」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1499
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_08dc6bc6:

    # ta "「I kinda feel like watermelon...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1348-1349)
    ta "\n「要是有西瓜和蜜瓜就好了。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1500
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_50e0d7e3:

    # ow "「The watermelon slices are here...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1351-1352)
    ow "\n「西瓜切好了哦-」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1501
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_e8c9fc9a:

    # "The farmer's wife brought out a bunch of\nwatermelon slices, cut like they would be for the\nObon Festival."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1354-1355)
    "阿姨将一大盘切好的西瓜，\n端到[漏れ]们面前。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1505
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_7ecd706a:

    # to "「Nice timing!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1358-1359)
    to "\n「nice timing」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1506
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_c1bb819b:

    # ta "「Don't mind if I do...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1362-1363)
    ta "\n「我不客气咯~」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1507
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b12605c3:

    # "Immediately, Tatsu-nii reached out and grabbed\na slice, biting right into it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1365)
    "辰兄迅速地，拿起西瓜就啃了起来。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1508
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_4d2220f6:

    # ky "「Tatsuki-san, you're eating too fast...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1367-1368)
    ky "\n「辰樹，你吃的太快了……」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1509
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_da27f7a7:

    # ow "「Big dragon boy, you really can eat.{p} I'm so happy you came by.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1370-1372)
    ow "\n「大只龙的小伙子，真的很能吃呢。\n有值得拿出来让你们吃的东西，真让我高兴呢。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1513
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_4fb2f7b6:

    # bo "「You guys got a real treat.{p} Did you save any for me?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1375-1377)
    bo "\n「你们不是在吃好东西嘛。\n当然有留我的那份吧？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1514
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b65df327:

    # fn "「Ehehe, we already ate it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1379-1380)
    fn "\n「诶嘻嘻，已经吃完了」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1515
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_f584be83:

    # "I'm tired, but doing this once in a while is fine.{p}When I'm working with everyone, it's like I'm a\nkid again, and I have a great time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1382-1383)
    "虽然很累，不过偶尔这样也不错呢。\n和大家一起工作就像是回到了我们小时候的那个时候一样，很开心呢。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1519
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_3647c18d:

    # ky "「Oh, it looks like the rain is clearing up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1386-1387)
    ky "\n「哦，看来像是雨过天晴了呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1520
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_60e61907:

    # "Before we knew it, the cloud above started to\nbreak up, and we could see a bit of blue sky\nthrough the gaps."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1389-1390)
    "不知道什么时候乌云就已经散去，\n能看到天空蔚蓝的颜色。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1521
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_648c8a51:

    # to "「Hey, look over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1392-1393)
    to "\n「看那边的天空。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1522
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_1e9e1732:

    # "Torahiko pointed in the direction of the mountain,\nand we all looked over."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1395-1396)
    "虎彦向着山的那边伸出手指，\n大家也一起朝那个方向看去。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1523
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_a82b546b:

    # fn "「A rainbow... it's so beautiful.」"
