    fn "\n「彩虹啊……真漂亮啊」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1524
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_3fd03e41:

    # fn "「How many years has it been since I've seen a\n rainbow this big and bright?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1401-1402)
    fn "\n「[漏れ]有多少年没看过这么大，这么漂亮的彩虹了呢」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1530
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_8d436b61:

    # ta "「It's a great scene...\n now, since we're done eating,\n Where are we going now?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1408-1410)
    ta "\n「真是好景色呢……好~肚子也填饱了，\n接下来去哪里玩吧！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1531
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_05b84f4f:

    # "Tatsu-nii stretched, patted his stomach,\nthen turned around to speak to us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1412-1413)
    "辰兄伸了个懒腰，梆梆地敲了敲自己的肚子，\n转过头来对大家说。"

# game/day 13.rpy:1532
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_4e75a0b3:

    # fn "「I'm so tired, I can't move.\n Forgive me...!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1415-1417)
    fn "\n「[漏れ]已经累得不能动了。\n放过[咱]----」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1533
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_0b6898e1:

    # ta "「Lazybones. You coming, Tora?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1419-1420)
    ta "\n「真不像样呢，虎会去的吧？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1537
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_e163ffe8:

    # to "「I'm too tired to move, too.{w} Next time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1423-1424)
    to "\n「我也已经累得不能动了。下次吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1538
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_c52cc81a:

    # ky "「It's not that you're tired,\n It's that you don't want to ride in his car,\n isn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1426-1428)
    ky "\n「大島其实并不是累了，\n只是不想坐辰兄开的车不是吗？」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1539
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_9d3cb7e5:

    # fn "「I can't move an inch, but it looks like Torahiko\n still has some energy left.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1430-1431)
    fn "\n「虽然[漏れ]是累得动不了，但是虎彦应该还能动的吧」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1543
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_1891990e:

    # to "「I really am tired right now.{p} Even if I wasn't, I still wouldn't want\n to get in a car with Tatsu-nii driving.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1434-1437)
    to "\n「我现在是真的很累啦。\n明明都这么累了，\n还要坐辰兄开的车。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1547
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_b1dc4114:

    # ta "「What was that?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1440-1441)
    ta "\n「原来如此」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1551
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_177e5f7b:

    # to "「I said, I. {w=.2}Don't. {w=.2}Want. {w=.2}To. {w=.2}Get. {w=.2}Into. {w=.2}Your. {w=.2}Car.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1444-1445)
    to "\n「所--以--说--我不想坐辰兄的车呀。」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1552
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_e538c29b:

    # ta "「Say that again!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1447-1448)
    ta "\n「你给我再说一次看看！」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1553
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_c51d2b4c:

    # ky "「Tatsuki-san, calm down.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1450-1451)
    ky "\n「喂，辰树君冷静一点」"

# game/day 13.rpy:1555
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki13_done_7ba787e0:

    # bo "「You guys are so energetic.\n It must be good to be young...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/辰樹_s_04.ks (KS 1455-1456)
    bo "\n「你们还真是精神呢。年轻真好啊……」"

